I"á<h1 class="no_toc" id="cleaning-procedures">Cleaning Procedures</h1>

<p>This page details the steps for cleaning the 7700 and 7200.  Always do the 7700 first, followed by the 7200.  You <strong>must</strong> clean the sensors before calibration.</p>

